{"tid":1059282,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"容祖兒祝福勝利 「希望佢冇事」","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T14:34:44.000Z","uid":196582,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8320b501432de8a9cb5833b01a3578c650c7cc","tid":1059282,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"容祖兒昨結束表演後接受訪問，表示收到勝利退出演藝圈的消息，很驚訝也很突然，覺得他是一個有才華的人，而《Pretty Crazy》原是合唱曲，自己和勝利都已經錄音，因牽涉很多後期製作，現在無法繼續合作，真的非常可惜。<br />\n她透露：「其實今天勝利會在現場與我合唱，但現在就沒有啦，<strong><ins>好多事情都趕不上變化，希望他沒事，</ins></strong>這件事我不應該說太多，他的公司應該也不希望我談論這件事。」<br />\n雖然合作告吹，但容祖兒表示這首歌花很多時間製作，自己也很喜歡，上周也已拍好MV，所以會繼續製作，暫定4月初推出。（陳明慧／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪唔知發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e891b403137bee0a17c1fb5f70fb12a9332eeff1","tid":1059282,"uid":7043,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"希望佢個人冇事姐<br />\n個人冇事先可以坐監嫁嘛"},{"pid":"929721cc5b2615cdef6860985dcce04d0e249db2","tid":1059282,"uid":163291,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"希望個罪犯無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8827107f866701df467145a12887b48ee33e3a","tid":1059282,"uid":213300,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"唔意外<br />\n英皇嘅人不嬲冇乜腦"},{"pid":"02c1052fe0083f4c8865c8d995ac31a676aec2a1","tid":1059282,"uid":112089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8615783cf7b24e4c7a1c7354a8b0497bee05ea","tid":1059282,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"又亂咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423ec4fc2e371b050c06f22761f65ee3fc306229","tid":1059282,"uid":31521,"like":0,"disli